ascents.name: Mandala sds
ascents.comment: This comment has nothing to do with Mandala.  Its just about two boys, both fat, both alone.  For two long years these boys quested out of fatness, unsuccessfully, I may add.  At the end of this arduous period there could only be one, Alan Nalitch.  But along the way these bullfrogs learned so much about the bodies of one another.  From the perils of the Chappies to the periodic 30 minute yaking they grew together.  While in the end there is only one Alan they both learned that Alan was inside of them all along and, to be frank, they should really get that checked out Alan is not really something you want inside of you for that long.  And while the world, or rather just 8a.nu, may have to say farewell to Shirley for a bit they can always get just a bit closer to him with just a subtle scratch of the buttock, in fact, I may just enjoy one such scratch myself.
